entries.meaning: (often in combination) Characteristic of a (certain type of) town.
(obsolete) Pertaining to or inhabiting a town, urban.
examples: In stature passing all the rest,A gallant girl for hewe;To be compared to townish nymphs,So faire she was to viewe.
